{"tha-ap215:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap215:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap215:0.3":"Saccasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap215:1.1":"“Vessabhu tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap215:1.2":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap215:1.3":"Deseti ariyasaccani, ","tha-ap215:1.4":"nibbapento mahajanam. ","tha-ap215:2.1":"Paramakarunnapattomhi, ","tha-ap215:2.2":"samitim agamasaham; ","tha-ap215:2.3":"Soham nisinnako santo, ","tha-ap215:2.4":"dhammamassosi satthuno. ","tha-ap215:3.1":"Tassaham dhammam sutvana, ","tha-ap215:3.2":"devalokam agacchaham; ","tha-ap215:3.3":"Timsakappani devesu, ","tha-ap215:3.4":"avasim tatthaham pure. ","tha-ap215:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap215:4.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap215:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap215:4.4":"saccasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap215:5.1":"Chabbisamhi ito kappe, ","tha-ap215:5.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap215:5.3":"Ekaphusitanamena, ","tha-ap215:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap215:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap215:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap215:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap215:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saccasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap215:8.1":"Saccasannakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}